      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(PricePoint that)
        Compares this object with the specified object for order. Returns a negative integer, zero, or a positive integer as this object is less than, equal to, or greater than the specified object. This method first compares the Price values of both PricePoints. Then it compares the demand values of both instances. The one with the highest value is the greatest.
